                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/5306: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-06-28T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 28, 1930—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>219. Legation’s 509, June 27, 3 p.m. Department authorizes concurrence.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
